author: Warhammer
description:
Focus Entertainment and Saber Interactive are excited to reveal their Year 2 plans for their multi-million seller Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2, starting with the release of the game’s Anniversary Update on September 4. 

Available now on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and PC, Space Marine 2 promises another year of free gameplay content, in addition to a new Season Pass bursting with new cosmetics. 

Check out our Year 2 Trailer!
